### ACTIVITY LOG ###
RewriteRule ^activity/read-with-limit$ controllers/developer/activity-log/read-with-limit.php [L] 

### PURCHASE ORDER ###
RewriteRule ^purchase-order$ controllers/developer/suppliers/purchase-order/purchase-order.php [L]
RewriteRule ^purchase-order/([0-9]+)$ controllers/developer/suppliers/purchase-order/purchase-order.php?id=$1 [L] 
RewriteRule ^purchase-order/active/([0-9]+)$ controllers/developer/suppliers/purchase-order/active.php?id=$1 [L] 
